short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Add labels to your inbox without leaving LinkedIn

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Enhance your LinkedIn experience with InLabels, a powerful tool designed to help you organize and manage your LinkedIn conversations effortlessly. Our extension allows you to:

Label Conversations: Easily apply customizable labels to your LinkedIn messages for better organization.
Streamline Communication: Quickly find and access important conversations with a simple labeling system.

With InLabels, you can stay on top of your LinkedIn interactions and keep your professional communications organized like never before.
